{"word":"First Fruits","slug":"first-fruits","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>First Fruits</b> First ripe of fruits, grain, oil, wine, and first of fleece, required as an offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=29'>Exo 22:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=16'>Lev 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=12'>Num 18:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=4'>Deu 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=5'>2Ch 31:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=35'>Neh 10:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=37'>Neh 10:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=39'>Neh 10:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=3&verse=9'>Pro 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=3'>Jer 2:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=11&verse=16'>Rom 11:16</a><br/> Offerings of:<br/> - Must be free from blemish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=12'>Num 18:12</a> <br/> - Presented at the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=29'>Exo 22:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=19'>Exo 23:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=26'>Exo 34:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=26&verse=10'>Deu 26:10</a> <br/> - Belonged to the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=20'>Lev 23:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=13'>Num 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=5'>Deu 18:5</a> <br/> Free-Will offerings of, given to the prophets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=42'>2Ki 4:42</a><br/> Wave offering of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=14'>Lev 23:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=17'>Lev 23:17</a><br/> As a heave offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=20'>Num 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=37'>Neh 10:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=30'>Eze 44:30</a><br/> To be offered as a thank offering upon entrance into the Land of Promise<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=26&verse=10'>Deu 26:10</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=23'>Rom 8:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=11&verse=16'>Rom 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=20'>1Co 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=23'>1Co 15:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=18'>Jas 1:18</a>"}]}